        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before marking a worker as failed, wrap individual worker calls with the exponential-backoff retry helper from the Error Propagation topic. Worker-level retries reduce noise in the error log without requiring the orchestrator to manage retry state explicitly."
          }
